Raspi-ShiftOut

This module implements a shift register implementation similar to that of the
Arduino SDK.

It is based on Device::BCM2835, which has C dependencies, so be sure to check
that you have the prerequisites to install that.

INSTALLATION

To install this module, run the following commands:

	perl Makefile.PL
	make
	make test
	make install

or simply:

    cpanm Raspi::ShiftOut

where cpanm is available, or with `cpan` where cpanm is not available.

SUPPORT AND DOCUMENTATION

After installing, you can find documentation for this module with the
perldoc command.

    perldoc Raspi::ShiftOut

If you think you have found undesirable or buggy behaviour you can check the bug
reports at Github.
    
    https://github.com/Altreus/Raspi-ShiftOut/issues

If you need more support you can try IRC.

    irc.freenode.org/#perl

